{"tid":798254,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"咩狗唔摸得頭?","createTime":"2018-08-29T07:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T05:25:27.000Z","uid":116709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8db1ccb0511476e1db693edac20a4945c8099ca7","tid":798254,"uid":116709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"非iq題, 上次係街見隻狗好可愛<br />\n諗著摸佢個頭,點知佢兇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b9889bb7b6dd51f92c2803fee677e8e6a22844","tid":798254,"uid":4231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"如果有人係街，見到你好可愛，所以摸你頭，你都兇佢啦"},{"pid":"8665e704c36185e3faae9145f9cd71f4658a634d","tid":798254,"uid":127929,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23869d11f2a7f54c9740a77a374efcac7ec4f863","tid":798254,"uid":82698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"將心比己 你一見到人會唔會即刻摸鳩人地個頭 人地一見到你就摸你個頭你點諗 不過隻隻狗唔同 摸下嘴下面頸側面多數都唔抗拒 好似係"},{"pid":"2626a80e7fb305e7993c1e33e66af3c3866bc52f","tid":798254,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"其實狗本身係唔鍾意俾人摸頭<br />\n因為摸得佢個頭嘅 佢就係承認你嘅地位高過佢<br />\n所以算係佢信任你嘅表現<br />\n佢唔俾你摸 代表佢唔相信你<br />\n<br />\n初初養狗 買咗幾本書睇<br />\n佢係咁講"},{"pid":"58330544499eb65eb9000be2a885650e5c41374e","tid":798254,"uid":176318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"老衲摸完會咬你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de40c05f6cbe5884b22621d0f71211e5628d0f9f","tid":798254,"uid":7323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:25:27.000Z","msg":"老衲，一摸<br />\n就打到你入人民醫院"}]}